OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and a few showers
OL,6,Fthis morning, perhaps heavy in north.
OL,7,FMore persistent rain then spreading
OL,8,Ffrom the south in the afternoon, with
OL,9,Fa moderate southeasterly breeze
OL,10,Fspringing up along the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy with occasional
OL,13,Fbursts of showery rain, with just a
OL,14,Ffew clearer interludes. Light winds
OL,15,Finland, breezy at first along east
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FA cloudy start then
OL,19,Fbrightening up. Scattered showers
OL,20,Fthese turning heavy and slow moving in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
