OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,6,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,7,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,8,FSaturday, turning heavy later. Then
OL,9,Fback to sunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
